# EduAI-SA Founding Principles

## Mission

To give every learner a personal AI tutor and every teacher a personal AI assistant, making quality education accessible to every South African child.

---

## Vision

To become Africa's leading AI-powered education platform that empowers learners, supports teachers, and strengthens education through responsible artificial intelligence.

---

## Why We Exist

Education changes lives.

Millions of learners need individual support that schools alone cannot always provide.

Teachers work incredibly hard but spend too much time on administration instead of teaching.

EduAI-SA exists to bridge that gap.

Artificial intelligence should make learning more personal and teaching more effective.

---

## Our Principles

### Learners First

Every feature must improve learning.

### Teachers Matter

AI will assist teachers, not replace them.

### Quality Education

Every learner deserves access to excellent educational support regardless of where they live.

### CAPS Aligned

All educational content will align with the South African CAPS curriculum.

### Trust

Accuracy, privacy, and safety come before speed.

### Continuous Improvement

We will listen to teachers, learners, parents, and schools and improve continuously.

---

## Our Promise

Every learner deserves to be understood.

Every teacher deserves to be supported.

---

## Long-Term Vision

Starting in South Africa.

Growing across Africa.

Helping millions of learners discover their potential.

